---
const repoUrl = 'https://github.com/Appels-to-oranges/thatstoobright';
const downloadUrl = `${repoUrl}/releases/latest/download/ThatsTooBright.exe`;
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon.png" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="ThatsTooBright is a lightweight Windows tray app that helps reduce late-night eye strain with smart brightness reminders."
    />
    <title>ThatsTooBright - Smart Brightness Reminders</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: dark;
        --bg: #070b14;
        --bg-soft: #0f1729;
        --card: #121b2f;
        --text: #ecf2ff;
        --muted: #9aaad1;
        --brand: #facc15;
        --brand-deep: #ca8a04;
        --line: #1f2a44;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Inter, "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 20% 10%, #243a6f66, transparent 40%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 80% 0%, #4b216966, transparent 30%),
          var(--bg);
      }

      .shell {
        width: min(1120px, 92vw);
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
      }

      .brand {
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.2px;
      }

      .hero {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
        gap: 22px;
        padding: 36px 0 22px;
      }

      .panel {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #172543cc, #111a2ccc);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 28px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem);
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        line-height: 1.08;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .btn {
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 12px 16px;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        transition: 0.16s ease;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        color: #1f1602;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-deep), var(--brand));
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        filter: brightness(1.03);
      }

      .btn-secondary {
        color: var(--text);
        border-color: var(--line);
        background: #10182b;
      }

      .stats {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .stat {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 16px;
        background: #0f182d;
      }

      .stat strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.45rem;
      }

      .features {
        margin: 24px 0 44px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .feature {
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 18px;
      }

      .feature h3 {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .donate {
        margin: 2px 0 20px;
      }

      .donate-card {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #121b2f, #10182b);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 14px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 14px;
      }

      .donate-card h2 {
        margin: 0 0 4px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .donate-card p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .donate-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        white-space: nowrap;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #1f1602;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-deep), var(--brand));
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        transition: 0.16s ease;
      }

      .donate-link:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        filter: brightness(1.03);
      }

      footer {
        margin: 8px 0 34px;
        color: #7483a9;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .hero {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .features {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .donate-card {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="shell">
      <header>
        <div class="brand">ThatsTooBright</div>
      </header>

      <section class="hero">
        <div class="panel">
          <h1>Smart brightness reminders for better nights.</h1>
          <p>
            ThatsTooBright is a lightweight Windows tray app that reminds you to dim your screen
            after your chosen time and threshold. Keep your eyes comfortable while you work late.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href={downloadUrl}>Download for Windows</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href={repoUrl}>View on GitHub</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <div class="stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>Configurable</strong>
              <p>Choose reminder time, brightness threshold, and snooze duration.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>Tray-first</strong>
              <p>Runs quietly in your system tray with optional startup behavior.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>Low overhead</strong>
              <p>Optimized polling and caching to minimize resource usage.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>One-click actions</strong>
              <p>Dim instantly, set to threshold, snooze, or skip from notification.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="features">
        <article class="feature">
          <h3>Context-aware reminders</h3>
          <p>Only triggers after your configured start time and above your brightness threshold.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <h3>Reliable startup controls</h3>
          <p>Enable launch at login and optionally start minimized directly to tray.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature">
          <h3>Native Windows toasts</h3>
          <p>Get actionable native Windows toast reminders with quick dim, threshold, and snooze controls.</p>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="donate">
        <div class="donate-card">
          <div>
            <h2>Support ThatsTooBright</h2>
            <p>If it helps your workflow, a small Ko-fi tip keeps updates coming.</p>
          </div>
          <a
            class="donate-link"
            href="https://ko-fi.com/paysoncarpenter"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >Donate on Ko-fi</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <footer>
        Built for Windows users who work late and want less eye strain.
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
